</p>
                                 </div>
                                 <div class="faq-item">
                                    <h5>Is Copado compliant with the latest European data protection laws?</h5>
                                    <p>Yes. Even though Salesforce (and Heroku.com, a salesforce.com company) has updated their license agreement with an Addendum that is compatible with the latest European laws, Copado has replicated their entire infrastructure in european heroku instances. By default, all customers go to the US instance, however please contact us to make the switch to EU.</p>
